rorism\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Clowney, Caroline. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.trackingterrorism.org/resource/university-chicago-chicago-project-security-and-terrorism-cpost\">\"Chicago Project on Security and Terrorism\"</a>. Global Terrorism Research Project, <a href=\"/wiki/Haverford_College\" title=\"Haverford College\">Haverford College</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">June 17,</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Chicago+Project+on+Security+and+Terrorism&amp;rft.pub=Global+Terrorism+Research+Project%2C+Haverford+College&amp;rft.aulast=Clowney&amp;rft.aufirst=Caroline&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.trackingterrorism.org%2Fresource%2Funiversity-chicago-chicago-project-security-and-terrorism-cpost&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AChicago+Project+on+Security+and+Terrorism\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Tinnes, Judith (2013). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.terrorismanalysts.com/pt/index.php/pot/article/view/270/html\">\"230 Websites and Blogs for Terrorism Research\"</a>. <i>Perspectives on Terrorism</i>. <b>7</b> (3)<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">June 17,</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Perspectives+on+Terrorism&amp;rft.atitle=230+Websites+and+Blogs+for+Terrorism+Research&amp;rft.volume=7&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.date=2013&amp;rft.aulast=Tinnes&amp;rft.aufirst=Judith&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.terrorismanalysts.com%2Fpt%2Findex.php%2Fpot%2Farticle%2Fview%2F270%2Fhtml&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AChicago+Project+on+Security+and+Terrorism\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Freedman, Benjamin (2010). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.terrorismanalysts.com/pt/index.php/pot/article/view/123\">\"Terrorism Research Centres: 100 Institutes, Programs and Organisations in the Field of Terrorism, Counter-Terrorism, Radicalisation and Asymmetric Warfare Studies\"</a>. <i>Perspectives on Terrorism</i>. <b>4</b> (5)<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">June 17,</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Perspectives+on+Terrorism&amp;rft.atitle=Terrorism+Research+Centres%3A+100+Institutes%2C+Programs+and+Organisations+in+the+Field+of+Terrorism%2C+Counter-Terrorism%2C+Radicalisation+and+Asymmetric+Warfare+Studies&amp;rft.volume=4&amp;rft.issue=5&amp;rft.date=2010&amp;rft.aulast=Freedman&amp;rft.aufirst=Benjamin&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.terrorismanalysts.com%2Fpt%2Findex.php%2Fpot%2Farticle%2Fview%2F123&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AChicago+Project+on+Security+and+Terrorism\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cpostdata.uchicago.edu/search_new.php\">\"Suicide Attack Database\"</a>. Chicago Project on Security and Terrorism<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">June 17,</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Suicide+Attack+Database&amp;rft.pub=Chicago+Project+on+Security+and+Terrorism&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcpostdata.uchicago.edu%2Fsearch_new.php&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AChicago+Project+on+Security+and+Terrorism\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Pape, Robert A.; O'Rourke, Lindsey; McDermit, Jenna (March 30, 2010). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2010/03/31/opinion/31pape.html?pagewanted=all&amp;_r=0\">\"What Makes Chechen Women So Dangerous?\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/New_York_Times\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"New York Times\">New York Times</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">June 17,</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=What+Makes+Chechen+Women+So+Dangerous%3F&amp;rft.pub=%27%27New+York+Times%27%27&amp;rft.date=2010-03-30&amp;rft.aulast=Pape&amp;rft.aufirst=Robert+A.&amp;rft.au=O%27Rourke%2C+Lindsey&amp;rft.au=McDermit%2C+Jenna&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2010%2F03%2F31%2Fopinion%2F31pape.html%3Fpagewanted%3Dall%26_r%3D0&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AChicago+Project+on+Security+and+Terrorism\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Steven L